# Repo-root environment (auto-loaded by `docker compose`). Copy to `.env` (gitignored).
# Only needed on restricted networks — on an open machine the defaults work.

# Postgres image source. On a locked-down machine, point this at the Artifactory
# (or internal registry) path that proxies the pgvector image. Must be a pgvector
# image (the migrations create the `vector` extension), NOT vanilla postgres.
# POSTGRES_IMAGE=artifactory.example.com/docker-remote/pgvector/pgvector:pg16
